instructions : 
download from github repository
install dependancies : apt install libpcre3-dev (required by swig),
                                    build-essential for g++ (required by swig)
                        tar xvfz swig (official site)
                        ./configure > make > sudo make install

                        SoX (audio conversion)
                        PortAudio or PyAudio (audio capturing)
                        ATLAS or OpenBLAS (matrix computation)
you are done.
cd swig
make
